{{page-title 'Egg Claims'}}
<h1>Egg Claims</h1>

<p>There are 35 eggs in this clutch, of which at least 3 are reserved as NPCs. Which three (or more) end up being the NPCs is up to whoever picks last -- there will be at most 32 players in this game.</p>

<p>Please choose a single egg and claim it by adopting it from this page (the roster). Use the information give to you to login to this character. If something goes wrong and you aren't able to use the password the game generates for you, please reach out to Shipfish on Discord or through a guest character.</p>

<p>Additional instructions will be sent to you automatically. To summarize, you must give your egg a descriptive or thematic name for use before your dragonet picks their personal name. For example, I think of egg #31 as the Star Sapphire Egg. You may get funky with it, but maintain decorum please.</p>


<ul class="nav nav-tabs">
{{#each this.model.roster as |group|}}

      <li class="nav-item"><a data-bs-toggle="tab" href="#{{group.key}}" class="nav-link {{group.active_class}}">{{group.name}}</a></li>
{{/each}}
</ul>

<div class="tab-content" role="tablist">    

{{#each this.model.roster as |group|}}

  <div id="{{group.key}}" class="tab-pane fade show {{group.active_class}}">

    {{#each group.chars as |char|}}
    
    <div class="roster-char-title">{{char.profile_title}}</div>
    

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col col-xs-12 col-sm-3">
          <CharIcon @char={{char}} />
      </div>
      <div class="col col-xs-12 col-sm-9">
          
          <p><AnsiFormat @text={{char.roster_notes}} /></p>
           
          
          {{#each-in char.fields as |field value| }}
          <div><b>{{field}}:</b> {{value}}</div>
          {{/each-in}}
          
          <p><b>Contact:</b> {{char.contact}} </p>
            
                  
           <div class="roster-char-warnings">
             
             {{#if char.app_pending }}
             <span class="badge bg-danger">App Pending</span>
             {{/if}}
             
             {{#if char.previously_played}}
             <span class="badge bg-info">Previously Played</span>
             {{/if}}
      
             {{#if char.app_required}}
             <span class="badge bg-warning">App Required</span>
             {{/if}}
            
           </div>
           
             
          <div>  
             <LinkTo @route="char" @model={{char.name}} class="btn btn-secondary">Profile</LinkTo>
             {{#if (not char.app_pending)}}
             <LinkTo @route="roster-claim" @model={{char.id}} class="btn btn-primary">Claim</LinkTo>
             {{/if}}
           </div>
             
        </div>
      </div>
    
    {{/each}}

</div>

{{/each}}

</div>

{{outlet}}
